items.title: Awesome Snmp
items.content_text:
### Libraries / Rust

*   [davedufresne/modern\_snmp (⭐28)](https://github.com/davedufresne/modern_snmp) - Modern SNMP is a pure-Rust library for SNMPv3. This repository includes snmp\_mp (SNMPv3 Message Processing) and snmp\_usm (Implementation of the User-based Security Model (USM) for SNMPv3) crates.
*   [Svedrin/sunt (⭐27)](https://github.com/Svedrin/sunt) - This repository implements an SNMP Agent written in Rust.
